        <mxCell id="kIgsmheDJQz7XmRfPmZH-13" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;font&gt;If all data is stored on a single machine, any network disruption — such as a router failure — could make that node unreachable, preventing the business from operating until connectivity is restored.&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
